                    <span>I had to deliver the eulogy at my mother's recent funeral service and this was without doubt the most difficult thing I have ever had to do in my life. However, after reading the book, I was able to say things that  otherwise I could not possibly have put into words. I was able to walk away  from the occasion knowing in my heart that I had said exactly what I had  wanted to say.<p>Without the support provided by this book I could not  possibly have done so. I offer you my sincerest thanks for the support  given by the book.<p>With grateful thanks, J. Wilson</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Thank You For Writing This Book!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
